import React from 'react'
import {
    SidebarContainer,
    Icon,
    CloseIcon,
    SidebarWrapper,
    SidebarMenu,
    SidebarLink,
} from './SidebarElements'
// import { FaBars } from 'react-icons/fa'

const Sidebar = ({ isOpen }) => {
    return (
        <SidebarContainer>
            <Icon>
                <CloseIcon />
            </Icon>
            <SidebarWrapper>
                <SidebarMenu>
                    <SidebarLink to="about">About Me</SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="work">Work & Education</SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="projects">Projects</SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="message">Message</SidebarLink>
                </SidebarMenu>
            </SidebarWrapper>
        </SidebarContainer>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
